  "title": "Performance Tester - Contract",
  "description": "<p><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong>:</p><ul><li>Define and implement performance testing strategies, plans, and scripts.</li><li>Collaborate with architects, developers, and business stakeholders to identify performance requirements and KPIs.</li><li>Lead performance test execution, analyze results, and identify bottlenecks.</li><li>Provide detailed performance reports and recommendations to technical and business teams.</li><li>Manage performance testing tools, environments, and data.</li><li>Mentor junior testers and coordinate with global QA teams.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Required skills:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Proven experience in performance testing and engineering</li><li>Hands-on expertise with tools such as LoadRunner, JMeter, NeoLoad, or Gatling.</li><li>Strong scripting skills (e.g., Java, Python, JavaScript).</li><li>Deep understanding of system architecture, performance tuning, and monitoring.</li><li>Excellent analytical, communication, and stakeholder management skills.</li></ul><p><br /></p>",
